* Auto\nLoader
** How it Works
***_ Tracks processed files via checkpoint
***_ Directory listing or file notification
***_ Exactly-once processing
** Capabilities
***_ Schema inference & evolution
***_ Handles billions of files
***_ Supports JSON, CSV, Parquet, Avro...
** Use Cases
***_ Log files arriving in cloud storage
***_ Data landing zones
***_ Ongoing incremental file ingestion
** Integration
***_ Works with Lakeflow Pipelines
***_ Works with Structured Streaming
@endmindmap
